msgid "Cooks food and keeps bees happy."
msgstr "Cozinha comida e deixa as abelhas felizes."

msgid "Campfires have multiple uses, including keeping bees happy, cooking raw meat and fish, and as a trap."
msgstr ""
"Fogueiras tem vários usos, incluindo mantendo as abelhas felizes, cozinhar "
"carne ou peixe cru, ou uma armadilha."

msgid "Campfire"
msgstr "Fogueira"

msgid "Soul Campfire"
msgstr "Fogueira de Almas"
